April 20, 1962. No. 814,

Misc.

Caulfield v. U. S. Department of Agriculture et al. /. D. DeBlieux for petitioner. Solicitor General Cox for respondents.

On petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fifth Circuit. Petition dismissed pursuant to stipulation under Rule 60 of the Rules of this Court.
